much still behind the fact

00:07:58.350 --> 00:08:00.800
that Finns are very literate,

00:08:00.800 --> 00:08:04.780
and they not only can
read, but they do read.

00:08:04.780 --> 00:08:11.950
And they love to read
different kinds of literature,

00:08:11.950 --> 00:08:16.760
and also factual literature.

00:08:16.760 --> 00:08:22.270
Reading is important,
and that is the area

00:08:22.270 --> 00:08:27.820
that I'm very worried
about also in Finland.

00:08:27.820 --> 00:08:32.230
People read less, especially
the young people,

00:08:32.230 --> 00:08:35.050
especially boys, read less.

00:08:35.050 --> 00:08:39.490 position:56%
And I think that's going to have --
unless we can do something about it,

00:08:39.490 --> 00:08:42.260
and I believe we can
do something about it,

00:08:42.260 --> 00:08:47.390
