00:30:35.970 --> 00:30:42.350
And just a little bit about the
lexicon of Finnish, but first,

00:30:42.350 --> 00:30:44.050
I want to talk a little
bit about English.

00:30:44.050 --> 00:30:47.860
So English is a Germanic
language, right?

00:30:47.860 --> 00:30:49.160
As we all know.

00:30:49.160 --> 00:30:51.500
So it's a Germanic language
