00:31:11.230 --> 00:31:13.230
and that came from
Greek, for example,

00:31:13.230 --> 00:31:14.890
French and Latin being
the bulk of it.

00:31:14.890 --> 00:31:17.720
Right? That's why that
newspaper article from

00:31:17.720 --> 00:31:19.530
"Le Monde" had so much overlap.

00:31:19.530 --> 00:31:23.110
Because really, English is
