00:32:06.110 --> 00:32:07.550
There's no pure language.

00:32:07.550 --> 00:32:10.160
So Finnish definitely -- even
though I showed that page

00:32:10.160 --> 00:32:13.110
where you saw that, you know,
Finnish looks sort of kind

00:32:13.110 --> 00:32:16.400
