00:32:16.400 --> 00:32:19.500
of languages over its
thousands of years of existence.

00:32:19.500 --> 00:32:21.830
So we have sort of
these strata in Finnish.

00:32:21.830 --> 00:32:24.870
And if we go from the bottom, the
bottom would be the native stratum.

00:32:24.870 --> 00:32:28.040
Those are words that are shared
