00:33:19.840 --> 00:33:21.990
with Germanic-speaking
peoples at that time.

00:33:21.990 --> 00:33:25.070
So we think of sort of these
strata as just like archaeology,

00:33:25.070 --> 00:33:27.050
the graphic there with
the archaeological layers.

00:33:27.050 --> 00:33:31.010 position:56%
Finnish has these layers in its
vocabulary of -- it has its basic --

00:33:31.010 --> 00:33:35.340
basic native stratum, and then
