01:26:52.480 --> 01:26:56.570
I'm allergic to computers,
so it's -- you know.

01:26:56.570 --> 01:26:59.400
So the Finnish brought over by the
immigrants also continued to live

01:26:59.400 --> 01:27:01.610
on in a number of areas
of daily life.

01:27:01.610 --> 01:27:04.200
The children of immigrants,
and their children, and so on,

01:27:04.200 --> 01:27:07.030
became further incorporated
into English-speaking life

01:27:07.030 --> 01:27:10.290
through public education,
employment, military service,

01:27:10.290 --> 01:27:14.010
inter-ethnic romances, and exposure
to mass media and popular culture.

01:27:14.010 --> 01:27:17.550
In 1937, Finnish-American scholar
John Komeinen [assumed spelling]

01:27:17.550 --> 01:27:18.850
notes these very factors

01:27:18.850 --> 01:27:22.830
in the language shift taking place
among the children of immigrants.

