Upper Peninsula a minute --

01:40:25.810 --> 01:40:27.740
upper Midwestern Finnish
communities.

01:40:27.740 --> 01:40:30.090
It comes out in local
Finnish-American festivals,

01:40:30.090 --> 01:40:34.590 position:56%
on Saturday night saunas, and in the
kitchen, baking [foreign language].

01:40:34.590 --> 01:40:36.370
Though researchers
have anticipated a day

01:40:36.370 --> 01:40:38.050
when Finnish will no
longer be spoken

01:40:38.050 --> 01:40:41.140
in the long-time Finnish stronghold
of the upper midwest, in ways great

01:40:41.140 --> 01:40:42.930
and small, it still persists.

01:40:42.930 --> 01:40:45.760
And it serves as a window to a
culture that persists as well.

